  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bcd, \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8 : \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b95\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Mysterious murder early in the morning when the husband and two children were at home: The husband fought the killer",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Polonnaruwa - A 42-year-old woman, the Chief Administrative Officer of the Lankapura Divisional Secretariat, was hacked to death in her house.",
        "Pulastipura Police said that the incident was reported at 2.30 am today (4) and the dead body was recovered from a room of his two-storeyed house.",
        "A mother of two, M.L. A woman named Yamuna Padmini has been murdered in this way.",
        "The police said that at the time of the murder, the woman's husband, a guard of a school, and their two children were present in the house and special investigations have been started as to why the said chief administrative officer was killed.",
        "The husband of the murdered woman told the police that he saw the killer in the dark and struggled with him, but the suspect escaped.",
        "In this situation, under the supervision of Polonnaruwa Senior Superintendent of Police Oshan Hewavitharana, Pulastipura Police Station Officer-in-Charge B.P.K. A police team headed by Pathrana has started investigations. No one has been arrested in connection with this murder till today (4) evening."
      ],
